tool_description: Search all India's RTO names by name, city PREFIX, like MH (for maharashtra), GA, CA, TA, etc
title: Indian RTO's Names Search

api_list.name: All RTO's
api_list.description:
Search for RTO names all over India,
you can use this API for autosuggestion
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://indian-rtos-names-search.p.rapidapi.com/rtos"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "indian-rtos-names-search.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
